♪ Flower, flower! ♪

302
00:25:41,090 --> 00:25:42,720
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

303
00:25:42,700 --> 00:25:44,380
How come I can do it?!

304
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:44,380
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

305
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:46,180
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

306
