♪ Flower, flower! ♪

326
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:15,760
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

327
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:18,920
Wow, I was able to do it too, Mother!

328
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,420
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

329
00:26:17,420 --> 00:26:18,920
♪ Flower, flower! ♪

330
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:23,100
Thank you, Linlin! Let's sing together!

331
00:26:23,100 --> 00:26:26,400
How interesting!
All right, I've decided.

332
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,810
I'm gonna set out to sea with her!

333
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:31,940
Nice! Nice!

334
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:31,940
A country where everyone is the same size...

335
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:36,440
and sits at the same eye level, and where everyone is equal.

336
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:42,990
All right, Linlin.
Let's build that country of dreams!

337
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:45,910
Count me in.

338
00:26:45,910 --> 00:26:47,160
Uh-huh!

339
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:54,280
Hey, look at this wanted poster!

340
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:57,740
Fifty million just for a little kid?!

341
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:00,540
How is that possible?

342
00:27:02,860 --> 00:27:07,200
A little girl destroyed the castle?!

343
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,500
The culprit is Charlotte Linlin!

344
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:15,240
Cipher Pol reported that she's dangerous!
She'll become a powerful force someday!

345
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,980
Catch her at any cost!

346
00:27:16,980 --> 00:27:18,550
Yeah!

347
00:27:22,930 --> 00:27:24,310
There she is!

348
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:28,020
Watch out, Linlin.

349
00:27:29,900 --> 00:27:32,030
I'm eating sweets!

350
00:27:33,690 --> 00:27:35,660
Don't interrupt!

351
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:49,240
Charlotte Linlin continued wreaking havoc

352
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:55,450
and became a worldwide threat seemingly overnight.

353
00:27:55,450 --> 00:27:57,120
She's a pirate!

354
00:27:58,240 --> 00:28:00,160
Run!

355
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:08,700
Bring me all the sweets you have!

356
00:28:08,700 --> 00:28:10,200
Your Majesty!

357
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,490
Oh, no!

358
00:28:11,490 --> 00:28:17,380
And then I'll guarantee you peace
and a country of dreams!

359
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:22,740
If you do as I say,
then everyone will be happy!

360
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:28,210
Those who disobey are just being selfish,
so I'll have to kill them!

361
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:31,970
Mother, I miss you...

362
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:35,180
I miss you!

363
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,230
Mother!

364
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:44,770
I'll make everyone big someday!

365
00:28:44,770 --> 00:28:48,360
Then we'll sit at the table together again!

366
00:28:48,980 --> 00:28:54,620
But there are still people who won't listen to me!

367
00:28:57,990 --> 00:29:01,930
I'm so sad and can't stop crying!

368
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:07,000
Because the only existing portrait of Mother...

369
00:29:07,500 --> 00:29:09,300
You're a good girl.

370
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:18,180
The one and only portrait of Mother
that was precious to me...

371
00:29:18,330 --> 00:29:20,600
was broken by them!

372
00:29:26,280 --> 00:29:29,730
I'll make them pay...
I'll make them pay...

373
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:34,030
Those Straw Hat Pirates!

374
00:29:42,910 --> 00:29:49,280
I'll never forgive them!

375
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:20,620
The plan has failed!

376
00:30:25,210 --> 00:30:28,380
What?!

377
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,630
They failed!

378
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:39,430
Listen, since I can fly,
I'll plunge on to the site with a mirror to escape!

379
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:45,060
Once you finish,
dive into Caesar's mirror quickly!

380
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:48,100
Well, here comes my part!

381
00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:49,700
Dammit!

382
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:51,800
She destroyed my launchers!

383
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:56,150
That monstrous hag!
She's definitely one of the Four Emperors!

384
00:31:07,710 --> 00:31:11,880
Retreat, everyone!
Jump into the mirror!

385
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:34,150
What incredible wind pressure!

386
00:32:18,190 --> 00:32:22,540
This is bad! We're stuck on the roof!
There's no way to escape!

387
00:32:25,050 --> 00:32:27,870
And there's no way to win, either!

388
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:42,750
Rook: In Voller Größe!

389
00:33:07,090 --> 00:33:08,390
What?!

390
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:51,200
Big Father!

391
00:33:54,670 --> 00:33:58,860
Oh, cool!
